{"tid":792163,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"見到個組仔帶左個動漫咕𠱸","createTime":"2018-08-24T10:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T14:31:13.000Z","uid":21456,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e00e9e947204c5af198d949c48bdfa17e0522025","tid":792163,"uid":21456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T10:47:53.000Z","msg":"大家都知宜家正值ocamp時期<br />\n岩岩帶完組仔組女玩完d野外定向就帶佢地番房放低背囊再去食飯<br />\n等D組仔組女出哂去我就入去check下有冇人再鎖門啦<br />\n點知見到其中一張床到放左個動漫咕𠱸<br />\n我心諗使唔使咁毒呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我就打算等陣玩房game之前睇下究竟邊個咁毒<br />\n再係玩房game果陣奚落下佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家有冇咩意見咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c589e22a8a68b6fa96cced2d11ac43ed0147bbcf","tid":792163,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5d8584dd6146f4ee0eca818d7bc309dfa67cce7","tid":792163,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T10:48:55.000Z","msg":"G 持"},{"pid":"1c5f250b34bccb8fa89e04b543c6dea0c29299c9","tid":792163,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T10:49:33.000Z","msg":"宜家出動漫咕𠱸應該好貴"},{"pid":"060bb420413def498dace6e108d028a1e7bd18be","tid":792163,"uid":31219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T10:50:27.000Z","msg":"收到飛個死毒撚係樓主嚟"},{"pid":"44c553885f017baef9368a1c371eb4c45801daf5","tid":792163,"uid":81308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:14:12.000Z","msg":"如果條友靚仔又有錢<br />\nd女咪照仆去幫佢含<br />\n關毒撚事咩"},{"pid":"159a030ba487457114844bf13ff9cbf79f518060","tid":792163,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"我諗我知你講邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g